HEADWORD: Skean
<hw>Skean</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ir <ets>sgian</ets>;
akin to Gael. <ets>sgian</ets>, W. <ets>ysgien</ets> a large knife, a
scimiter.]</ety> <def>A knife or short dagger, esp. that in use among
the Highlanders of Scotland. <altsp>[Variously spelt.]</altsp></def>
⟦ldquo⟧His <xex>skean</xex>, or pistol.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
